@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_uenmng(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v1 + 0.89)) / wp.abs((v0 + 0.82 + tmp + 0.09)))
    v2 = wp.cos((0.30 + (tmp + 0.95 + v1 + 0.24)))
    v0 = (wp.exp(0.51) - (wp.cos(tmp + 0.88) * wp.cos(v0 + 0.26)))
    data[tid] = v0
